                  <p>Being the FOURTH SESSION in the Mayoralty of The Right Hon. 
                  <persName id="t17850406-84-person936">
                     RICHARD
                      CLARK
                  <interp inst="t17850406-84-person936" type="surname" value="CLARK"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17850406-84-person936" type="given" value="RICHARD"></interp>
