               Death
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17850406-84-person940">
                  MARY
                   JONES
               <interp inst="t17850406-84-person940" type="surname" value="JONES"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17850406-84-person940" type="given" value="MARY"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17850406-84-person940" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
             
                  <rs id="t17850406-84-verdict408" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17850406-84-verdict408" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY of uttering the indenture knowing it to be forged
            </rs>, <rs id="t17850406-84-punish409" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17850406-84-punish409" type="punishmentCategory" value="death"></interp>
