               <p>Tried by the Second London Jury before Mr. 
               <persName id="t17850406-84-person941">
                  Baron
                   EYRE
               <interp inst="t17850406-84-person941" type="surname" value="EYRE"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17850406-84-person941" type="given" value="Baron"></interp>
